; HyBBX v2.0.0 — INI topology templates (pick one, copy to hybbx.ini)
;
;   hybbx-standalone.ini.example   Main + local TNC (one host, lab/single-box)
;   hybbx-main.ini.example         Main only — RF on remote Secondary
;   hybbx-mesh.ini.example         Main + mains_proxy mesh + remote Secondary
;   hybbx-secondary.ini.example    Secondary RF host (pairs with main or mesh)
;
; Default install uses hybbx-main.ini.example. Full keys: docs/MANUAL.md
